Tommhs_Meltable_Rock_Ice.name = Meltable Ice Block
Tommhs_Meltable_Rock_Ice.description = [TMP] <color is="#7EDCFF"><b>MELTABLE ICE BLOCK</b></color>\n<color is="#C9C9C9"><i>“Lay the cold, place the torch — and the water obeys.”</i></color>\n\nA farmer’s shortcut for canals, moats, and irrigation.\nPlace it like a normal block, then put a <color is="#ffffff"><b>torch nearby</b></color> to melt it into <color is="#4FB6FF"><b>water</b></color>.\n\n<color is="#6F6F6F">────────────</color>\n<color is="#ffffff"><b>Tip:</b></color> Build the whole channel with ice first, melt everything in one go.\n<color is="#ffffff"><b>Note:</b></color> Melts when a torch is placed close to it.